105
00:04:38,445 --> 00:04:40,530
Ton père a 8 restaurants.
Laisse couler.

106
00:04:40,655 --> 00:04:41,822
Salut les nuls !

107
00:04:43,971 --> 00:04:45,826
Cole, t'as amené les diapos ?

108
00:04:46,061 --> 00:04:47,111
Oh mince.

109
00:04:47,236 --> 00:04:48,935
J'allais justement commencer,

110
00:04:49,060 --> 00:04:50,979
et mon pote Boots
m'appelle et me dit

111
